	<body><a name="top"></a>
		<center><h1 style="font-size: 240%;">MTG Image</h1></center>
		<p style="margin-top: 1.0em;">This project provides <a href="http://www.wizards.com/Magic/">Magic the Gathering</a> card images and symbols for developers to easily use in their projects.<br>
		<br>
        For more details see: <a href="#documentation">Documentation</a> and <a href="http://forums.mtgsalvation.com/showthread.php?t=561388">Discussion Thread</a><br>
        <br>
		Any bugs or feedback, e-mail me at <a href="mailto:robert@cosmicrealms.com">robert@cosmicrealms.com</a><br>
		</p>
		<br>
		<br>
